true,"voteup_count":8,"content":"\u003cp\u003e这个应该是目前保送北大清华最难的方法了小伙子。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562972763,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"f646acd002fada674c41225ffe55bb4c","url_token":"lan-luan-lang","name":"滥乱浪","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-cd9f146b12697f64b4cc34c3cb7c7237_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-cd9f146b12697f64b4cc34c3cb7c7237_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/f646acd002fada674c41225ffe55bb4c","user_type":"people","headline":"追求智慧","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562972763","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546167833,"updated_time":1546167833,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e小伙子你这样问不对\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我见过你打听河北大学数学系的问题\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e要是你只有数学强，其余科都只是河北大学的水平，毫无疑问，你会在清华北大挂科挂到死。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以你应该这么问：我证明了哥德巴赫猜想，我能去清华北大当教授吗\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e之所以不提MS和PHD，是因为我感觉几年之内你不会有阅读英文数学论文的能力。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e好好脚踏实地吧，我见过很多小有名气的数学工作者本科上的也并不是名校。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561085218,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561085218","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545914941,"updated_time":1545914941,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"\u003cp\u003e2019年1月1日\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e      题主首页:\u003ci\u003e 知乎live\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ci\u003e《教你如何炒作:炒作的三大要素》\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ci\u003elive描述:我是如何从0粉短时间内吸粉14k+，\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ci\u003e并获取各路大V关注，引起知乎热烈讨论。\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003e\u003ci\u003e   99.9元/人\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e 是不是数学鬼才不知，我倒是希望被打脸。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559909237,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"660afb9bf85c7793d2496470360cd5d6","url_token":"liu-yu-he-38","name":"中华稀瓜","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-269e4e0edba3920924c926817dd712ab_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-269e4e0edba3920924c926817dd712ab_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/660afb9bf85c7793d2496470360cd5d6","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559909237","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545793031,"updated_time":1546070434,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"\u003cp\u003e以我本人对高中经历的了解，个人认为， \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hash=\"7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\"\u003e@证明\u003c/a\u003e 你有很大的可能性是在抖机灵。十八岁上下正是搞事的大好时光，比如当年，我们把可乐瓶盖大小的钠块扔进小便池，还有人把足球大脚开进路边的车窗里。在知乎组织一场闹剧，这鬼捣的规模远超我们当年，可是危险系数几乎没有，还是可以理解的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不过即使没有人身伤害，网络暴力的能量也超乎大家想象，看看德国boy的经历你就懂了。希望你日后，能够因导演这场闹剧而得到更多的成长，并且产生的心理阴影尽可能少。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e（12月27日追加）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e今早看到了你的这篇声明：\u003ca href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/53378543\" class=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003ehttps://\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"visible\"\u003ezhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/53\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003e378543\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"ellipsis\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我的态度是，不管那位匿名答主是谁，如果你本着抖机灵的态度掀起这场风波，你都不会承认他是你的老师。所以，我的看法不变。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e（12月29日追加）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e目前看到题主的动态，似乎真的去看了些论文机构。但在此我劝题主尽快收手，你的机灵抖得太大，有些刹不住。这样下去，我担心你在元旦收到的网络暴力强度、以及潜在的人肉搜索危险。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e须知，德国boy的初衷是好的，尚且受十几年的网络暴力困扰、而且中途还出现了很久的心理问题；你相比他，积极的成分小太多，你将遇到的攻击，很有可能比他的极端得多。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563150619,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"c79b646c1d11afefbbe0b672ddcc22d9","url_token":"wante","name":"欧属","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f871e5a79034d2dad71197c6dddc78c6_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f871e5a79034d2dad71197c6dddc78c6_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/c79b646c1d11afefbbe0b672ddcc22d9","user_type":"people","headline":"奶油与糖浆万岁！","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563150619","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546186393,"updated_time":1546186426,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"\u003cp\u003e吃了好久的瓜，我觉得最后的结果就会是题主发表论文，然后一堆大手群体狂欢开始找喷点开始写文，然后一堆高赞。就算是题主有可嘉奖的思路也会被大概率忽视，然后过个一两天，开始有大v出现平复大众情绪，说要鼓励、多支持高中生孩子，然后这事慢慢平息，前提是题主发论文不透露个人信息的情况下。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果题主没发论文，那题主会被骂爆，总有闲人、满脑子压抑情绪的人会去人肉题主，然后嘲讽，这事会拖很久。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e总的来说，题主还是发论文的好，损失不如不发的大。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560970039,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"7d35d835d40f30cf4829e1a1b8582a50","url_token":"jun-mo-qi-30","name":"君莫泣","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-1b44f8374676b24f2bb225094d508d58_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-1b44f8374676b24f2bb225094d508d58_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/7d35d835d40f30cf4829e1a1b8582a50","user_type":"people","headline":"牛逼师","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560970039","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545903193,"updated_time":1545903193,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我他么特意下了逼乎app为了看您的猜想！\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560335714,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560335714","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545830178,"updated_time":1545830492,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"\u003cp\u003e建议你放弃对哥德巴赫的证明，好好学习竞赛课程吧。争取竞赛搞出成绩获得保送或者降分的资格，不一定非要去北大清华数学系，但一定要去一个好一点的985的数学系，这样才可以获得一些资源。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这是我真心实意的建议。因为对于一个想要从事数学研究的人而言，环境太重要了，连付云皓这样的IMO两次获得金牌的人目前想进入前沿数学的研究都有难度，如果考不上好一点的大学的数学系，几乎只能沦为民科。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e研究哥德巴赫猜想对绝大多数人而言（包括99%的北大数学系教授）几乎等同于浪费时间，因此这会让你离“好的环境”越来越远。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560797184,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560797184","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545888749,"updated_time":1545888749,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"\u003cp\u003e会。前提是你的证明是严谨正确的，并且能被学术界承认。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在未公开前请你仔细检查自己的证明是否足够严谨，并确保证明中没有任何自以为是的“常识”，往往这些一笔带过的“常识”才是证明中最具有本质难度的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e年轻人对于数学有热情是值得鼓励的，但希望你在研究一个问题前先足够的了解它，毕竟有无数个水平远远凌驾于清华北大水平之上的天才对此也苦苦思索而不得解之。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不过，如果你是伽罗瓦转世，就当我没说。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560469744,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"7f5e8d9357c6b62eb14821bb81267708","url_token":"mei-yuan-tao","name":"用户名","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/7f5e8d9357c6b62eb14821bb81267708","user_type":"people","headline":"学生","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560469744","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545840281,"updated_time":1545840281,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":10,"content":"\u003cp\u003e问这样的问题，佩服你也欣赏你，不论你证明正确与否，我要承认你现在真的是在学数学，我高中学的，那叫考试。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559877219,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"766e58e3d7ba864ab61c0aea2ec15704","url_token":"avon-zhang","name":"Avon","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-129f6f8b8c8af5e0ab8118b242aaa170_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-129f6f8b8c8af5e0ab8118b242aaa170_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/766e58e3d7ba864ab61c0aea2ec15704","user_type":"people","headline":"一句话描述","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559877219","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545790637,"updated_time":1546089135,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":11,"content":"\u003cp\u003e您放心，清华北大不会保送的，做系主任还行。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不过您至少也是普林斯顿和巴黎高师终身教授了\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e菲尔兹奖和阿贝尔奖都可以破格发给您，以后在人类数学长河中，您就是高斯前面那一位哦。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e放心 中科院都是小事情，北大会为您成立一个由您冠名的数学中心。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e-----------------------------\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e以上是对问题回答，以下是对一些回答的质疑。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在很多回答里 我看到很多人同情这名高中生（下文用他指代），你们说得对 ，包括我在内的很多人质疑他，甚至于讥讽挖苦他，对，说的没错。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我们是在讥讽 讥讽他的傲慢与无知，讥讽有很多人依旧大言不惭而言之凿凿相信奇迹，热爱总是好事情。这都8102年了，哥猜难不难？地位高不高？没有数论代数基础能不能看懂一些基础分析？这些问题难道百度不出来吗。他难道看不到那么多优秀数学研究者的劝告吗！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e古往今来，无数数学大家，哪个不是天才，从未听说过哪个人有如此傲慢荒唐之言辞。他这是热爱吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他这是民科。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这不是几千年前了，苹果掉下来 了，你说你发现了万有引力 。看到有的车加速快，你说这可以看作加速度。 看到磁针旋转，你说你想到了电磁感应。这是8102年了！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e私以为，他可以说哥猜被证明了，因为数论的很多难题是看似很简单的，初中水平也可以了解。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是证明，却要求非常高的水平，如果不是攻读pure mathmatics方向的硕士，其他数学方向硕士也很难理解并且深入研究。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在我看来，假如扔给他近世代数，点集拓扑的有难度的习题，他便不会继续叫嚣都被证明了。讲到底，还是无知。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后，送给那些圣母们一句谏言，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你只看到了我们嘲讽他，却看不到他把纯粹数学按在地上摩擦！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e科学是严肃的，不是拿来玩弄的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e有位知友说得好，任何一次民科和吃瓜群众的狂欢，都会导致国民科学素养的一次倒退。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后，两道思考题共勉。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e先想想怎么证明0.999999--=1\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e先想想√2+1怎么证明为无理数\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e以上。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561451845,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0da44b5a81d13502f1b4d17240ae3937","url_token":"wu-yi-kai-57","name":"双V加成","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f0d8721fa92368faa1fd08ba6450202e_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f0d8721fa92368faa1fd08ba6450202e_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0da44b5a81d13502f1b4d17240ae3937","user_type":"people","headline":"东川路学渣","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561451845","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e92c4a72274f2b7da74ff886ebb5a0c9_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545968603,"updated_time":1546233098,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":6,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我想知道这是哪个天才提的兄弟问题：\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/307121693\" class=\"internal\"\u003e如果一个初中生统一了四大基本力，那么可以保送山东蓝翔吗？\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我还是太年轻。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-a984715bd99da4aba72f4ad87f71a56e_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"396\" data-rawheight=\"4096\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-fa713c9a67d3a16e6776a4cc3d93b5d1_b.jpg\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"396\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='396'%20height='4096'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"396\" data-rawheight=\"4096\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-fa713c9a67d3a16e6776a4cc3d93b5d1_b.jpg\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"396\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-a984715bd99da4aba72f4ad87f71a56e_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561549899,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"5974e58382034822e7920b76ab3410fd","url_token":"tao-lei-yi","name":"是阿毅啊","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d563584020b0bf9cfaed1b354c7dbf1d_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d563584020b0bf9cfaed1b354c7dbf1d_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/5974e58382034822e7920b76ab3410fd","user_type":"people","headline":"执着于PPT的PPT菜鸟","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561549899","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545977722,"updated_time":1545977722,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":6,"content":"\u003cp\u003e如果题主真能证明得出，我就在本回答的评论中随机抽中一位关注我的知友，赠送iPhonexs一台，绝不食言。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560224624,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"d2d156cbd8c2c303240412611de46cae","url_token":"obersteinlee","name":"obersteinlee","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-bc438bd7f11c09dffe5bead96e8d9e23_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-bc438bd7f11c09dffe5bead96e8d9e23_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/d2d156cbd8c2c303240412611de46cae","user_type":"people","headline":"人虎","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560224624","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545820026,"updated_time":1545820026,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":6,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我辈以心证道，可以去起点发表\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561926830,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"8980d37769465f49ad5f2bfb1fcac69e","url_token":"ban-zhi-jun","name":"半知菌","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4856daff56c951e902cbda0346f2f732_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4856daff56c951e902cbda0346f2f732_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/8980d37769465f49ad5f2bfb1fcac69e","user_type":"people","headline":"文昌鱼","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561926830","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546015644,"updated_time":1546015644,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":6,"content":"如果我能打破跳远的世界纪录，我会有资格被选进省队吗？如果我长得和吴彦祖小李子一样帅，校花会不会对我另眼相看？事实上，证明哥德巴赫猜想这个事件的意义和难度要远远大于保送什么的行为，所以我认为这是一个荒唐的命题。其实问题者认为保送本身就是一个终极理想的人生目标，从而寻求一种超自然的外力达到对目标征服的意淫。\u003cbr\u003e可是，你知道真正的天才是怎么样的吗？当伽罗华在孤独而凄冷的深夜，面对着即刻的死亡，在纸上潦草而绝望地挥洒自己无与伦比的数学天赋的时候，他可能宁愿自己不是那个天才。当梵高的眼前只有混乱而绝美的星夜，颤抖的笔触无法触及爱人的心灵，旷世的才华却被巴黎美院的专家踩在脚底，他可能宁愿自己不是那个天才。伟大的天才要忍受伟大的不幸。他们想得到世人的认可，谋求一个被社会公允的“位置”时，他的天赋的发泄却早已远远超过那个无聊的位置，到了高的光明之处，就像高飞的伊卡洛斯，他们从不在乎明亮的阳光会烧灼自己闪亮的羽毛。","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562761465,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"edc75a415396fcc93605e5a5140c0dca","url_token":"gu-dian-28-85","name":"瓜皮","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-57f7add4ebb5eef2e3e6e9c2d6289f89_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-57f7add4ebb5eef2e3e6e9c2d6289f89_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/edc75a415396fcc93605e5a5140c0dca","user_type":"people","headline":"秃子","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562761465","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546143109,"updated_time":1546181992,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":10,"content":"\u003cp\u003e2019年元旦你最关心的事情是\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e○群主女装了没有?\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e○能不能收到元旦礼物？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e○中美合拍的西游记上映了没有？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e●逼乎的高中生能否证明哥猜？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e————————————————————\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e怎么这么多圣母婊，TM哥德巴赫猜想在数学界就跟广大数学工作者的亲女儿似的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e有一天，一个毛头小子出来问:“我娶了你女儿能被清北保送吗？”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这些个“老岳父”们并没有生气，答道:“”娶了’我女儿’是何等的荣耀，只怕你到时候还看不上保送清北，问题是200多年来，无数的青年才俊都失败了，你有什么本事能够娶到？”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e结果这小子直接给大佬们挨个通知:“1月1日我就要把你们女儿给睡了”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这不是找骂吗？？？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而且大佬们都没想继续搭理他，稍微懂点数学的人也不过出来嘲讽他两句。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e嘲讽两句怎么了，这么点反对的声音都听不下去那就不要到知乎来哗众取宠。这儿又不是学术平台，这儿只是沙雕网友们来找乐子的地方。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560773883,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"be22805c13096b079ab5e00fc80faa80","url_token":"ning-meng-cha-shui-ban-fen-tian","name":"柠檬茶水半分甜","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-194ce648bd3b1f9c8fd30a41e092a579_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-194ce648bd3b1f9c8fd30a41e092a579_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/be22805c13096b079ab5e00fc80faa80","user_type":"people","headline":"总得有人去做。","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560773883","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545886641,"updated_time":1545886641,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"\u003cp\u003e能……甚至能到超出你的期待。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果成功证明，我给予你最大的祝福。我们会普天同庆这个世界难题就此解决，是由我们中国人解决。这足以给中国乃至世界数学界带来翻天覆地的变化。一切荣耀背后，我们会是第一批见证的人；\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果没有成功，希望你保持平常心。数学有天赋很难得，剩下的时间里，若你足够努力仍有进入高等学府的机会。接触了更高一层的知识后，你可再进行研究推演。网上的言论或许会把你淹没，那就卸了吧。沉淀下来，一点点的努力。你还是个孩子，你有无限的可能。我同样祝福你。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562129111,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"f9a23194de041b8f1f7346f0294f5819","url_token":"a-feng-34-23","name":"阿疯","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/f9a23194de041b8f1f7346f0294f5819","user_type":"people","headline":"工程师","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562129111","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546055928,"updated_time":1546104126,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我只是一个键盘数学家，不过我猜高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想不会被数学系录取。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e证明哥德巴赫猜想有多难我不知道，不过可以横向比较下。数学隐士格里戈里-佩雷尔曼证明证明庞加莱猜想。(因为格里戈里-佩雷尔曼真是隐居了，所以称为数学隐士。)\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e庞加莱猜想（Poincaré conjecture）是法国数学家庞加莱提出的一个猜想，是克雷数学研究所悬赏的七个千禧年大奖难题。其中三维的情形被俄罗斯数学家格里戈里·佩雷尔曼于\u003cb\u003e2003年左右证明\u003c/b\u003e。\u003cb\u003e2006年，数学界最终确认佩雷尔曼的证明解决了庞加莱猜想。\u003c/b\u003e庞加莱猜想是一个拓扑学中带有基本意义的命题，将有助于人类更好地研究三维空间，其带来的结果将会加深人们对流形性质的认识。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e格里戈里·佩雷尔曼在花了\u003cb\u003e8年时间研究这个足有一个世纪的数学难题\u003c/b\u003e后，在2002年11月和2003年7月之间，将3份关键论文的手稿粘贴到\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//arXiv.org\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003ehttp://\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"visible\"\u003earXiv.org\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e这个专门刊登数学和物理预印本论文的网站上，并用电邮通知了几位数学家，声称自己证明了几何化猜想。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，大概是初中发论文，小学3年级你就开始研究这些高深谜题。小学3年级就开始研究这些高深的数学猜想，你大概率小学毕业就被中科大少年班挖走了，还上什么高什么中。你根本就没有机会上高中。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果你证明了任何数学猜想，直接发稿这个网站\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//arxiv.org\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003ehttp://\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"visible\"\u003earxiv.org\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e免得被中科院的守门老大爷为难。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560771130,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"e6c58a8ffed3fc3571fca06069d35a26","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560771130","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545886396,"updated_time":1545886462,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"content":"\u003cp\u003e看了这么多的回答，总结一下。有冷嘲热讽的，有劝题主好好学习上个好大学的，有吃瓜群众的，有坐等见证历史的。但是最重要的一点是，有没有新的数学概念或理论诞生。以题主的知识来看，如果你是用初等数学解决了这个问题，对数学的推动或贡献可能微不足道。毕竟数学猜想的难题的价值不在于有多难，而是在解决的过程中能启发人们产生新的数学概念或理论。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e举个例子，许多数学家如高斯欧拉都没能证明费马大定理，于是有人劝希尔伯特去解决这个难题，他却说不想杀死这只下金蛋的鹅。为什么他这么说？因为在对费马大定理长达三个世纪的求证过程中，诞生了许多数学概念和理论，还开拓了新的数学分支。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e瞧，问题不在证明之后会不会带来保送，职位，经济等无关数学的东西。而是证明本身带来了什么，能够促进我们对数学的理解？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559858203,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"364dd70a48f9d91e4e8162c21dad9549","url_token":"zhong-xiang-97","name":"MaDaoXPlus","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-735805838dbdfa5a85c5febcbfac416f_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-735805838dbdfa5a85c5febcbfac416f_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/364dd70a48f9d91e4e8162c21dad9549","user_type":"people","headline":"节能主义者","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559858203","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545789081,"updated_time":1545792290,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"content":"\u003cp\u003e放心在元旦之前绝对不会举报你，最近刚好无聊得很。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=340\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=300\u0026sort_by=default","totals":2142}}
